= How to open a Port in {{gateway_product_name}} Firewall =
== How to open an Incoming Port in {{gateway_product_name}} Firewall from the Outside ==
For purpose of allowing an incoming connection on {{Gateway product name}} originating from,

* if using VM: the host.
* if using physical isolation: the internet.

{{Firewall Custom}}

{{Firewall Settings}}

Add. Replace <code>80</code> with the actual port you would like to open.

{{CodeSelect|code=
EXTERNAL_OPEN_PORTS+=" 80 "
}}

Save.

{{Reload_Firewall_ws}}

== How to open an Incoming Port on {{gateway_product_name}} for Connections Originating from {{Workstation product name}} ==
For purpose of allowing an outgoing connection from {{Workstation product name}} to {{gateway product name}}.

{{Firewall Custom}}

Might be useful for [[Tor#Additional_SocksPorts|Tor additional <code>SocksPort</code>s]].

{{Firewall Settings}}

Add.

Note: Replace <code>9230</code> with the actual port you would like to open. Replace <code>SOCKS_PORT_CUSTOM</code> with <code>SOCKS_PORT_ANOTHER</code> when using multiple. Replace word <code>ANOTHER</code> with another unique word.

{{CodeSelect|code=
SOCKS_PORT_CUSTOM=" 9230 "
}}

Save.

{{Reload_Firewall}}

